  <p>I would look at an offering from SuperMicro. LOTS of folks resell their servers (ASLab, NewEgg, etc). They are fairly reliable and are generally priced well. It generally is just a barebones lacking CPU, memory, or disk space, but that will give you some flexibility in cost structure.</p>
